data.description: This Glennbrooke beauty is loaded with luxurious upgrades. This Brunswick floor plan showcases spacious rooms, abundant storage, a HUGE screened rear porch and an attached 2-car garage. The main level impresses with 10' ceilings, 8' doors, and rich wood flooring. The grand gourmet kitchen features quartz countertops complemented by a herringbone tile backsplash, top-of-the-line stainless appliances including a gas cooktop.  An oversized pantry, a work island with a breakfast bar, and a sizable breakfast room. The oversized family room offers a cozy gas log fireplace, and a nearby half bath adds convenience for guests. The main level is also home to the owner's suite with attached bathroom boasting a double sink granite-topped vanity, a freestanding soaking tub, a separate shower, and a roomy walk-in closet. Upstairs houses a separate living area, spacious bedrooms with an abundance of storage and 2 additional bathrooms. Step outside to discover a relaxing outdoor space with the screened porch and hot tub! Glennbrooke is an exclusive community offering a clubhouse, two pools, a splash pad, a scenic pond with walking trails, a pavilion with an outdoor fireplace and grill, and an expansive green space complete with soccer goals and a baseball backstop. Convenient to shopping and interstates!
